metadata.name: Road to Freedom
metadata.description:
Without freedom there is no creativity. Without creativity there is no art. Without art there is no expression. Without expression there is silence.

This is a tribute to a small island in the Philippines called Siargao, where I began to not only explore the beauty around me but also to begin delving into my own truths. Without the freedom this island afforded me, I wouldn't be the person I am today.
